<p><strong>CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY.</strong> </p>

<p>We reserve the right to change this Privacy Policy at any time and at our own discretion. We will disclose the date on which this Privacy Policy was most recently revised in the “Last Updated” legend at the top of this page indicates. We encourage you to review this Privacy Statement periodically so that you remain aware of any changes. By using this Service after these changes have been posted, you accept this Privacy Policy as revised. Any revisions, changes, or updates to this policy are immediately effective for all new users and will be effective 30 days after posting for existing users.</p>



